OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start to the day but
OL,6,Fstaying mainly dry with some bright
OL,7,Fspells developing. A few light showers
OL,8,Fare possible over northern counties
OL,9,Flater in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA largely dry evening with
OL,12,Fjust the odd light shower around.
OL,13,FMainly dry with clear spells overnight
OL,14,Fbut some showers will spread
OL,15,Fsouthwards later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA lot of dry and bright
OL,18,Fweather with sunny spells and light
OL,19,Fwinds. A chance of one or two light
OL,20,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
